{"tid":364620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同165高嘅女仔扑嘢 翻唔到轉頭","createTime":"2017-08-18T14:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T07:53:30.000Z","uid":71198,"like":22,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3434a87e8159866abeb0fbad1e6322048af758e","tid":364620,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"本人屌過好多150-160 越矮感覺越差<br />\n150果啲對腳短到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要唔知係咪報大數<br />\n可能得14x 侏儒咁<br />\n自從同過165高嘅女仔屌完<br />\n先知道之前果啲150-160全部都係殘障<br />\n發育不健全咁<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布所有160或以下嘅女人都係殘障<br />\n<br />\n利申 181<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1487ff397d7868880f9c2a89c0755b8f5e32215c","tid":364620,"uid":38194,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"165好普通姐<br />\n170 up 就真係堅正，企喺度對住塊連身鏡推車啱啱好<br />\n<br />\n利申180"},{"pid":"b19b64dd9b826c9bbc93fb1f466e90a2baf08dd4","tid":364620,"uid":4531,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fda651f632635c3a97b98e55a15f9de7cd24b74","tid":364620,"uid":71198,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>165好普通姐<br />\n170 up 就真係堅正，企喺度對住塊連身鏡推車啱啱好<br />\n<br />\n利申180</blockquote><br />\n170 我未試過 ，最高果件168都幾好<br />\n150果件真係人生污點，留翻俾侏儒仔屌算"},{"pid":"8c93efad263606763efe2c6af1499276002ff5fa","tid":364620,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下咩原因令你鐘意侏儒？"},{"pid":"81bdbcfb7990a0ab680f2917cd5e07f591e17dc6","tid":364620,"uid":71198,"like":9,"dislike":26,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">我正式宣布所有160或以下嘅女人都係殘障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s